    "created_at": "2026-03-19T00:00:00.000Z",
    "notes": "PANIC DETECTOR + REVERSAL BUYER. Three-phase logic: (1) DETECT: spot_change_pct < -1% AND VIX >= 17 AND PCR > 1.3 \u2014 genuine panic (not just a dip). Buy slightly OTM PE (0.45 delta) to ride the momentum. (2) RIDE: hold PE as long as spot continues falling. Partial exit at 25% PE profit if VIX starts reverting. (3) FLIP: when PCR becomes extreme (>2.0) or VIX crosses below 20, close PE and open CE for the bounce \u2014 markets almost always bounce after a panic spike. ELSE branch: if the initial condition is a spike UP instead (short squeeze, geopolitical relief rally), does the opposite \u2014 buys CE on the spike. Hard exit at VIX>=30 (circuit breaker territory \u2014 no directional conviction possible). Max loss per day: \u20b93000. Best used on days like: Iran escalation, China border tension, sudden FII sell-off, circuit breaker approach."
  },
